      "committedDate": "2026-06-11T02:50:08Z",
      "messageBody": "Adds Dealix commercial OS layers, sales machine, CRM assets, founder\noperator scripts, governance docs, and daily execution tooling.\n\nSourced from the V1-V5 backup (dealix-v1v5backup.zip). Integrated\nadditively — no existing files were overwritten — and verified end-\nto-end on this branch before opening for review.\n\nHighlights\n- Web app pages: brand, cases, command-center, daily-draft, data-room,\n  delivery-os, kpi-finance, lead-engine, offers, partner-room,\n  persuasion-room, pipeline, pricing, revenue-machine, sales-assets,\n  war-room, automated-sales, client-acquisition, plus /api routes.\n- API surface: middleware (ip_allowlist, metrics, privileged_audit),\n  security (mfa, mfa_policy, oidc, saml, scim), routers\n  (commercial_ops_router, payments_router).\n- Business OS: acquisition, ai, analytics, brand, ceo, client-portal,\n  closing, conversion, crm, data-room, delivery, finance, governance,\n  industries, launch, lead-lists, legal-lite, offers, persuasion,\n  pricing, proof, proposals, reports, retention, review,\n  sales-automation, sales-machine, scoring, and supporting _data,\n  _generated.\n- Founder operator scripts: dealix_daily_operator, dealix_v4_run_all,\n  dealix_v5_run_all, generate_* (board pack, client brief, conversion\n  scorecard, daily CEO brief, delivery plan, expansion offer,\n  followup queue, founder dashboard, launch brief, monthly client\n  review, ops health, outreach drafts, proof report, proposal,\n  prospect pack, quote, retention risk, sales call notes,\n  sales machine pack, ultimate sales OS pack, weekly command,\n  weekly operating review, workflow review agenda), verifiers\n  (verify_company_os, verify_crm_pipeline, verify_dealix_ultimate_os,\n  verify_delivery_os, verify_sales_machine, verify_ultimate_sales_os,\n  verify_client_acquisition_delivery_os), and approval gates\n  (approve_outreach_draft, reject_outreach_draft, mark_*).\n- Doctrine tests: no_auto_send, no_guaranteed_revenue_claims,\n  commercial_claim_safety, commercial_offer_mapping,\n  agent_permission_safety, payment_handoff_requires_approval,\n  payment_pricing_safety, pricing_requires_approval,\n  proposal_requires_qualified_opportunity, walk_away_rules,\n  whatsapp_safety_gates, customer_success_handoff_required,\n  outbound_safety_gates, partner_model_margin_rules.\n- CI workflows: agentic-security-gate, client-acquisition-delivery-\n  check, dealix-ultimate-os-check.\n- Reports tree expanded across 30+ domains (ai_governance, ai_ops,\n  analytics, business_os, commercial, customer_success,\n  data_governance, data_products, data_room, enterprise,\n  enterprise_sales, execution, final, finance, infra, legal,\n  localization, offers, operator, ops, outreach, partnerships,\n  privacy, procurement, product, productized_services, security,\n  whatsapp).\n- learning_flywheel/, self_evolving_os/, intelligence_os additions,\n  templates/contracts, autonomous_growth (api, case_study_pipeline,\n  content_calendar, seo_cluster_engine, social_proof_aggregator).\n\nFix\n- apps/web/tsconfig.json: add baseUrl + paths \"@/*\" so the @/ alias\n  imports the new pages depend on resolve. Without this, `next build`\n  fails on multiple modules (lib/company-os, lib/sales-machine,\n  lib/sales-automation, lib/generated/*).\n- apps/web/app/lead-engine/page.tsx: fix wrong import — PERSUASION_ANGLES\n  lives in lib/sales-automation/lead-sources, not lib/sales-machine/\n  ultimate-sales-os. Without this, typecheck errors.\n\nHygiene\n- Excluded from the merge: .pytest_cache, .ruff_cache, .worktrees,\n  .mavis, node_modules, .next, __pycache__.\n\nVerification (all green on this branch)\n- python3 scripts/check_no_secrets.py            -> No secrets found\n- python3 scripts/verify_dealix_ultimate_os.py   -> verification passed\n- python3 scripts/dealix_daily_operator.py --mode demo -> 7/7 steps OK\n- python3 scripts/production_readiness_check.py  -> 5/5 checks passed\n- (cd apps/web && npm install && npm run typecheck && npm run build)\n  -> typecheck clean; build succeeded with all new pages prerendered.\n\nDo NOT merge to main until CI is green on this PR.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01CiamJCEcmQ9RQUTk7BHtst",
